### Example Usage of a VDC Backup with 2 policy sets
```hcl
resource "cloudavenue_backup" "example-vdc" {
  type = "vdc"
  target_name = cloudavenue_vdc.example.name
  policies = [{
      policy_name = "D6"
    } ,{
      policy_name = "M3"
     }
  ]
}
```

